{"text_id":173909,"tokens":["Great"," question","!"," From"," a"," psychological"," perspective",","," it"," is"," true"," that"," humans"," are"," capable"," of"," being"," indoctr","inated"," into"," believing"," anything",","," no"," matter"," how"," immoral"," it"," might"," seem","."," There"," are"," several"," factors"," that"," contribute"," to"," this",","," such"," as"," cognitive"," biases",","," social"," pressure",","," and"," emotional"," manipulation",".","\n\n","Cognitive"," biases"," refer"," to"," the"," many"," ways"," our"," brains"," automatically"," distort"," our"," perceptions"," of"," reality","."," For"," example",","," confirmation"," bias"," causes"," us"," to"," seek"," out"," information"," that"," confirms"," our"," existing"," beliefs",","," while"," ignoring"," evidence"," that"," contradicts"," them","."," This"," can"," make"," it"," easier"," for"," us"," to"," accept"," false"," or"," misleading"," information",","," particularly"," if"," it","'","s"," presented"," in"," a"," convincing"," way",".","\n\n","Social"," pressure"," is"," another"," factor"," that"," can"," lead"," people"," to"," adopt"," beliefs"," that"," they"," might"," not"," otherwise"," hold","."," This"," can"," include"," everything"," from"," wanting"," to"," fit"," in"," with"," a"," particular"," group",","," to"," feeling"," pressure"," from"," authority"," figures"," or"," peers"," to"," conform"," to"," a"," certain"," worldview","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," people"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," conform"," to"," group"," norms"," when"," they"," believe"," that"," their"," peers"," are"," watching"," them"," or"," they"," fear"," rejection"," from"," the"," group",".","\n\n","Finally",","," emotional"," manipulation"," can"," also"," play"," a"," role"," in"," indoctr","ination","."," Cults"," and"," other"," authoritarian"," groups"," often"," use"," intense"," emotional"," experiences"," to"," create"," a"," sense"," of"," belonging",